    <h2>🔥 Vulnerabilities</h2>

    <p>🔓 <b>SureTriggers Plugin Flaw Enables Admin Account Creation</b><br>
    Improper validation of ST-Authorization lets attackers exploit API. Patch immediately.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/news/wordpress-plugin-flaw-exploited-4/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🕵️‍♀️ <b>Chrome 136 Fixes 20-Year History Leak Flaw</b><br>
    Partitions `:visited` links to block cross-site tracking. Feature available via flags in earlier builds.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/chrome-136-fixes-20-year-browser-history-privacy-risk/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
