  <div class="news-item">
    <h2>🕵️ Adversaries & Attacks</h2>

    <p>📱 <b>Malware Found in Preloaded Apps on Fake Phones</b><br>
    Spyware on cheap Androids steals wallets, scans recovery phrases. Over $1M stolen.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://hackread.com/pre-installed-malware-cheap-android-phones-crypto-fake-whatsapp/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🦠 <b>ResolverRAT Targets Healthcare and Pharma Firms</b><br>
    Uses AES encryption, DLL hijack, IP rotation. Detected in six countries.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://securityaffairs.com/176537/malware/new-malware-resolverrat-targets-healthcare-pharmaceutical-firms.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>📦 <b>Malicious NPM Packages Steal PayPal & Crypto Credentials</b><br>
    “tommyboy_h1/h2” used install hooks to exfiltrate credentials. Fortinet urges cleanup.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://securityaffairs.com/176530/security/malicious-npm-packages-to-steal-paypal-credentials.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🧧 <b>Earth Bluecrow Deploys BPFDoor Linux Backdoor</b><br>
    Uses BPF filters to evade detection. Controller supports stealthy reverse shell access.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/research/25/d/bpfdoor-hidden-controller.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🇵🇰 <b>SideCopy Expands to Target Indian Critical Ministries</b><br>
    New CurlBack RAT and Spark RAT used with advanced evasion tactics.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://thehackernews.com/2025/04/pakistan-linked-hackers-expand-targets.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
